cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and semantic similarity, which are typically covered in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and cybernetics (cs.CY). The paper specifically focuses on improving the correlation of vector space models with human judgments, which is a common evaluation metric in these sub-fields.
